ism.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/26302/', '', 'Opium, Diphenoxylate, Morphine, Difenoxin', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Simeprevir, Cabotegravir, Zanamivir, Velpatasvir, Etravirine, Dolutegravir, Oseltamivir, More', 1767369485);
